msgid "Slots Helper"
msgstr ""

#: ../../components/templating/helpers/slotshelper.rst:7
msgid ""
"More often than not, templates in a project share common elements, like the "
"well-known header and footer. Using this helper, the static HTML code can be"
" placed in a layout file along with \"slots\", which represent the dynamic "
"parts that will change on a page-by-page basis. These slots are then filled "
"in by different children template. In other words, the layout file decorates"
" the child template."
msgstr ""

