#: ../../components/templating/helpers/slotshelper.rst:56
msgid ""
"The :method:`Symfony\\\\Component\\\\Templating\\\\PhpEngine::extend` method"
" is called in the sub-template to set its parent template. Then "
":method:`$view['slots']->set() "
"<Symfony\\\\Component\\\\Templating\\\\Helper\\\\SlotsHelper::set>` can be "
"used to set the content of a slot. All content which is not explicitly set "
"in a slot is in the ``_content`` slot."
msgstr ""

